description:
Melissa McCarthy [Bridesmaids, The Heat, Mike & Molly, Spy, Superintelligence, Can You Ever Forgive Me?] joins Anna from Australia to talk about avoiding the pandemic (and saltwater crocs), being a parent, working with her husband, the brilliance of John Candy, the importance of having pockets, the value of comedy and more. Later in the episode Anna is joined by OB/GYN and Twitter’s unofficial resident gynecologist, Dr. Jen Gunter.

Learn more about Dr. Gunter and her book The Vagina Bible at her website drjengunter.com

Please subscribe to Anna Faris is Unqualified on Apple Podcasts and follow us on social media:

Music by: Mondo Cozmo @mondocozmo
